               <p>MR. BOLLAND conducted the prosecution.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270712-60-person439">
                  JOHN 
                  THOMPSON
               <interp inst="t18270712-60-person439" type="surname" value="THOMPSON"></interp>
